<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>猫眼电影后台管理系统</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/themes/ui-pepper-grinder/easyui.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/themes/icon.css">
    <style>
        .logo {
            height: 150px;
            width: 100%;
            background: url('img/20180122144914.jpg') 0 1px;
            opacity:0.9;
        }

        #logoLeft {
            text-align: center;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 60%;
            float: left;
        }

        #logoRight {
            height: 100px;
            width: 40%;
            float: left;
        }

        #logoLP {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #DDD9E0;
            position: relative;
            top: -12px;
        }

        #h1 {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #DDD9E0;
        }

        #logoP {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #DDD9E0;
            margin: 80px 0 0 0;
            position: absolute;
            right: 100px;
        }

        .nav {
            text-align: center;
            width: 200px;
        }

        .panel-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .nav>ul {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(189, 189, 189, 0.67);
        }
        .nav>ul>li {
            height: 40px;
            line-height: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(189, 189, 189, 0.67);
            border: 1px solid gainsboro;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #000000;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .nav>ul>li:hover {
            background-color:rgba(138, 96, 34, 0.67);
        }

        #pBtn {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="easyui-layout">
    <div class="logo" data-options="region:'north'">
        <div id="logoLeft">
            <h1 id="h1">猫眼电影后台管理系统</h1>
            <p id="logoLP">Maoyan Movie Background Management System</p>
        </div>
        <div id="logoRight">
            <p id="logoP"><span id="IheaderSpan">包丕龙</span>,你好啊！<span id="pBtn">安全退出</span></p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div id="nav" class="nav" data-options="region:'west',title:'功能列表',split:true">
        <ul>
            <li data-name="users">用户管理</li>
            <li data-name="message">资讯管理</li>
            <li data-name="movie">电影管理</li>
            <li data-name="cinema">影院管理</li>
            <li data-name="cinemaMatch">院线匹配管理</li>
            <li data-name="hotMovie">热映电影管理</li>
            <li data-name="reflect">即将上线管理</li>
            <li data-name="hotShow">热播影视管理</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="Ishow" class="easyui-tabs" data-options="region:'center'" style="background:#eee;">
    </div>
    <div data-options="region:'south',title:'项目团队介绍',split:true" style="height:80px;font-size:12px">
        <p style="margin:5px 0 0 0;text-align:center;">开发人员：王鑫、曾豪、王晓媛、周绍凤、黄义武、杨硕、杨全生</p>
        <p style="margin:5px 0 0 0;text-align:center;">运用了Visual Studio Code、mongodb、Google Chrome等开发工具</p>
    </div>


    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery.easyui.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/datagrid-groupview.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/datagrid-detailview.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/ajaxfileupload.js"></script>
    <script src="js/main.js" type="module"></script>

</body>

</html>